  "3060630": {
    "name": "修仙：但系统让我种田",
    "steam_appid": 3060630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妖魔乱世，万道崩毁，而我唯一的修仙路，竟然是拿起锄头种田？欢迎来到《<strong>修仙：但系统让我种田</strong>》，一个融合了冒险、养成、探索与田园生活的世外桃源。在这个妖魔横行的乱世，你将逃离血腥的战场，在修行者的庇护所——桃源村，开启一段“以农入道”的奇幻生活。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>官方Q群：1019884016、1044856827（已满）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望你能留下宝贵的意见，我们是听劝的工作室~有趣的东西我们会添加上去，错误的点我们也会修改。希望能和你一起完善这款游戏！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>官方B站空间：1113796124</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在b站个人空间后面输入这段数字，也可复制BV号：<strong>BV1NZghz3EPK</strong>，直接粘贴在<strong>bilibili</strong>主链接后跳转</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心玩法：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>系统与修仙：</strong>莫道修仙路漫长，系统随身定乾坤。通过天赋觉醒掌握各种技能，你将彻底打破传统修行的枷锁，在系统助推下，于瞬息万变的战场中开启一段无敌的飞升传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb10bc0cf93941d8f68c534b60399e6f.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>农耕与播种：</strong>远离乱世喧嚣，在桃源村中，你将体验到播种的乐趣。每天给韭菜浇水，看着它们茁壮成长，这种与自然共舞的感觉将让你忘却外界的纷扰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/763c2441d7808bd3f564269b416d0585.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与打怪：</strong>莫道农夫手无力，系统加身斩神魔。穿梭于光怪陆离的禁忌之地，凭借随机觉醒的天赋与神技，对妖魔开启一场华丽的降维打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/7682dfaf40a04ee193078a167d7155bc.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>修炼与突破：</strong>道修仙易，生死在瞬息。当灵气凝练至临界点炸裂时，那是凡人向仙道的跨越！系统助你窥见灵脉流转，却无法替你挡住幽幽心魔。守得住那一线清明，便是筑基大成的神威；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/b17c21da7fc380cfac175f77443aaf77.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守不住，则是道心崩坏、功亏一篑的绝望惨烈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/871dd57b239064b65f4162035638048b.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>任务与挑战：</strong>奔走于桃源村，每一桩村民的委托都是你扎根于此的因果。在解决生存危机的同时，你的抉择将时刻牵动身边红颜的情思。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/cb6cea517658e881a45d791d97bf87a6.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当好感积累至满溢，换来的不仅是修行至宝，更是解锁那些隐秘在月色下、令你怦然心动的深度羁绊与温存时刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0a27fe030c48b4ab1def6bdd2bb3bb9e.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>垂钓与探险：</strong>探索地图的每一片水域，享受垂钓的宁静与乐趣。水域中隐藏着丰富的鱼类和宝藏，每一次垂钓都是一次新的探险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/1be1e19464f1cae307d762f7ca219d1c.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多结局剧情：</strong>游戏中的剧情丰富多样，玩家的每一个决定都可能改变剧情的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/c5107c339ad69df8d1b9a7190171f19e.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择将决定你的命运，也将影响桃源村的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/5237f779755e57decb54bdb52ad1a4c9.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心跳与心动</strong>：关于爱与谎言的危险博弈。在多重情感关系中寻求平衡，享受步步惊心的“心跳时刻”。莫要心存侥幸，那位对你有着极度占有欲的她，早已识破你所有的伪装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/664660354b407df19bed0923ea7ab611.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>服装与武器：</strong>执神兵，披战衣，在这崩坏的世界里活出尊严。探索荒野不仅是为了生存，更是为了搜集那些散落在禁地的上古套装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.poster.avif?t=1770187059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.webm?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060630/extras/0658745ae9b2905adfeff2e8aa69f6fb.mp4?t=1770187059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色亮点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>系统修仙：</strong>系统重塑仙道根基，逆天天赋随心觉醒。 告别枯燥苦修，凭借强力技能化繁为简，让原本坎坷的求索之路在你挥指间变得纵横无碍、势不可挡。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>修行者庇护：</strong>桃源村由修行者庇护，充满了神秘与古老的传统。你将在这里学习到各种修行知识，提升自己的能力，斩妖除魔，为自己增添修为。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>女性角色互动：</strong>每个女性角色都有独特的性格和故事背景，与她们互动将为你带来丰富的情感体验。提高好感度不仅能获得奖励，还能解锁更多剧情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实农耕体验：</strong>游戏中的农耕系统真实模拟了播种、浇水、收获等过程，让你真正感受到农耕的乐趣和成就感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>水域探险乐趣：</strong>地图上的水域广阔而神秘，每一次探索都可能发现新的鱼类和宝藏。垂钓不仅是一种休闲方式，更是一种挑战和冒险。</p></li></ul>",
